subproject.description:
Output 1: Appropriate tools and training are made available to support GHG Inventory Systems, NAMAs and in the context of national priorities
Output 2: Targeted technical support is provided as necessary to national teams for the implementation of project activities
Output 3: Support provided for the identification of innovative policy and financing options for low-emission development in order to facilitate partnerships between the Public Sector and Industry
Output 4: Knowledge and lessons learned disseminated to raise awareness, engage stakeholders, and inform decision-makers
